description: Serving up Serbia's most delicious dishes in the Denali and Healy areas, Moose-AKa's is making mouths water with their marvelously delicious family recipes. Their fried crepes are crazy tasty, and their ever-so-flavorful Moussaka is an absolute must-try.  You’ll also find a wonderful selection of savory soups, Sopska salad with fresh veggies that are perfectly crisp, and so much more. Count on Moose-AKa’s authentic cuisine to make any day extra awesome.
name: Moose-AKa's
